{"title":"Wolf Tooth ReMote 360º Dropper Lever Gives You All the Positions","link":"https://bikerumor.com/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-lever/","date":1701138856000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1600\" height=\"1068\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-6.jpg\" alt=\"wolf tooth components remote 360 dropper lever\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-6.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-6-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-6-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-6-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-6-768x513.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-6-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-6-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>The new Wolf Tooth Components ReMote 360 uses a joystick-style lever with a universal clamp to let you position it anywhere, any way you like. Put it under or over, left or right, it’ll work around whatever else you have on your bar and fit your ergonomic preferences. Here’s how it works…</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-2.jpg\" alt=\"wolf tooth components remote 360 dropper lever\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-2.jpg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-2-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-2-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-2-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-2-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The design pulls cable from the center, rocking on the joystick’s edges in any angle you push it. That mounts on a swiveling base, which can also rotate around the handlebar.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2426\" height=\"992\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-1.jpg\" alt=\"wolf tooth components remote 360 dropper lever\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-1.jpg 2426w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-1-297x121.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-1-800x327.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-1-120x49.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-1-768x314.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-1-1536x628.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-1-2048x837.jpg 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The swivel mount is grooved to lock into place once you clamp it on to the bar, letting one bolt do all the work. The cable end slides into the lever and secures with a small bolt on its backside. A barrel adjuster provides fine-tuning.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1068\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-4.jpg\" alt=\"wolf tooth components remote 360 dropper lever\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-4.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-4-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-4-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-4-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-4-768x513.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-4-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-4-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The beauty of the design is also that you can mash it down, press it forward like normal, or even pull it up.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1061\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-5.jpg\" alt=\"wolf tooth components remote 360 dropper lever\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-5.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-5-297x197.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-5-800x531.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-5-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-5-768x509.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-5-1536x1019.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Work around any big displays or mounts…</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1068\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-3.jpg\" alt=\"wolf tooth components remote 360 dropper lever mounted on right side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-3.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-3-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-3-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-3-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-3-768x513.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-3-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-seatpost-remote-lever-3-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>…or just put it on the other side if you have a big suspension lockout lever taking up left-side bar space. It pulls up to 8mm of cable, making it compatible with most dropper posts.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Price is $59.95, black and pewter only. Available now.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.wolftoothcomponents.com/products/remote-360\" target=\"_blank\">WolfToothComponents.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wolf-tooth-remote-360-dropper-lever/\">Wolf Tooth ReMote 360º Dropper Lever Gives You All the Positions</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"5881685586b91fb6b1cae7b7164f2e812aa8ff157eeae78914bb6547726acfe9","category":"Cycling"}